c 上之后，苹果最近似乎加大了对游戏的投入，随后又推出了<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/death-stranding-directors-cut-is-coming-to-the-mac-175801242.html"><em>《死亡搁浅》</em></a> 。人们是否愿意在 iPhone 上玩（或支付全价）此类主要游戏则是另一回事。不过，苹果公司吸引 Capcom 和 Ubisoft 等主要发行商参与其游戏业务的事实无疑值得注意，尤其是当我们期待 Apple Vision Pro 的首次亮相时。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-event-2023-live-updates-on-the-new-iphone-15-160001658.html"><em>在这里</em></a><em>关注 Apple “Wonderlust” 活动的所有现场新闻</em><em>。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/assassins-creed-mirage-death-stranding-and-resident-evil-village-are-coming-to-iphone-15-pro-183325896.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/assassins-creed-mirage-death-stranding-and-resident-evil-village-are-coming-to-iphone-15-pro-183325896.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 622ad2c7-咖啡馆-4907-a280-b947698c9208</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2023 18:33:25 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694543842</ingested><modified> 2023-09-12T18:37:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/3caf4670-5199-11ee-bf3f-d4673beffea4" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><med